	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is a great item and i applaud the VI programers for making it.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sure everyone wants to spout off about how high level casters don't melee and that is true on the face of things.  However, a lot of high level casters will get a big kick out of this item.  For a Shaman, Druid or Chanter, this item rocks on stats alone.<br><br>The life of a caster can get pretty boring - nuke, nuke, nuke, stun, med, med, med.... lather, rinse, repeat...etc.  That will remain the same no  matter how much haste you get in tough zones and on serious raids.  This is more for having FUN or in solo/kiting situations where you might save a little mana.  It offers some variety, a chance to taunt melee's with a FBSS since you have a better haste item, etc.  I'm an SK primarily and I am happy to see this in the game.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Andred D'Nocte<br>Grave Lord<br>- Fennin Ro - </td></tr>
